July 18, 2021

July 18, 2021
**Updated on: 27 July 2021**

This document is an appendix to the research report “Forensic Methodology Report: How to catch NSO Group’s
Pegasus” published as part of the Pegasus Project.

This document may be updated over time as additional individuals become public.

## Appendix D: Pegasus Forensic Traces per Target

All individuals have been assigned a code name for safety and privacy reasons. Only individuals who have given
consent will be named publicly.

The occurrence of a known malicious iCloud account may be a result of actions made by a Pegasus customer against
a potential target device. It does not by itself signify that an attack was attempted or succeeded.
